@startuml
title State Machine: Case Status

[*] --> Open
Open --> UnderInvestigation : assign detective
UnderInvestigation --> SuspectIdentified : evidence found
SuspectIdentified --> ArrestMade : warrant executed
ArrestMade --> Prosecuted : DA files charges
Prosecuted --> Convicted : court verdict
Prosecuted --> Closed : case dismissed

UnderInvestigation --> Closed : insufficient evidence
SuspectIdentified --> UnderInvestigation : new leads
ArrestMade --> UnderInvestigation : new evidence
Convicted --> Closed : sentencing complete

Open --> Inactive : no progress
Inactive --> UnderInvestigation : new information
Inactive --> Cold : prolonged inactivity
Cold --> UnderInvestigation : breakthrough

Closed --> [*]

note right of UnderInvestigation
  Active investigation phase
  Evidence collection
  Witness interviews
  Lead follow-up
end note
@enduml
